room_title: Escape room "Fallout" by Novus Escape Room in Dover
room_description: Project Fallout, an aptly named weapon of mass destruction is reported missing along with the group of scientists working on it. You wake up to find that you have no memory of who or where you are, but you are being interrogated by unknown authorities about a weapon you have no recollection of. You heard the authorities say that you wiped out your own memory before their arrival. Now you know that you have to escape from their captivity and find out who you are, and what happened.
